303
00:26:33,005 --> 00:26:33,571
No.

304
00:26:34,281 --> 00:26:35,802
I’m going to talk to him.

305
00:26:35,963 --> 00:26:37,200
Don’t, Kawi!

306
00:26:38,698 --> 00:26:39,458
Just don’t.

307
00:26:43,315 --> 00:26:44,555
You can just talk to me.

308
00:26:46,975 --> 00:26:48,440
You two can go check in on Not.

309
00:26:52,996 --> 00:26:53,586
Pear.

310
00:26:53,586 --> 00:26:54,290
What are you doing?

311
00:26:55,782 --> 00:26:56,626
What do you want?

312
00:26:58,769 --> 00:26:59,547
Pear.

313
00:27:00,893 --> 00:27:05,137
Do you know when he was dating you, he refused to break it off with Kwan?

314
00:27:05,733 --> 00:27:07,733
Do you even know you’ve been fooled?

315
00:27:14,725 --> 00:27:16,044
You do, don’t you?

316
00:27:17,814 --> 00:27:18,932
- Then why–
- I’m pregnant.

317
00:27:22,758 --> 00:27:24,481
