318
00:27:26,916 --> 00:27:28,513
Things have come this far.

319
00:27:30,196 --> 00:27:31,717
There’s no turning back for me.

320
00:27:34,558 --> 00:27:35,827
But don’t you worry.

321
00:27:37,148 --> 00:27:41,417
