322
00:27:42,906 --> 00:27:44,263
Why Pear?

323
00:27:45,473 --> 00:27:46,494
Why?

324
00:27:46,494 --> 00:27:48,347
At least Not offers me my future.

325
00:27:52,940 --> 00:27:54,360
Today, I’m getting married.

326
00:27:56,180 --> 00:27:57,852
And soon, I’m having my own family.

327
00:28:00,655 --> 00:28:01,567
What about you?

328
00:28:03,836 --> 00:28:05,252
What can you offer me?

329
00:28:10,693 --> 00:28:15,441
How many times did I tell you when we were together?

330
00:28:16,107 --> 00:28:17,628
