343
00:29:12,918 --> 00:29:16,758
But as we grew older, lived our lives, and continued to make mistakes,

344
00:29:18,730 --> 00:29:22,848
we'd have to accept that this was the farthest we could achieve.

345
00:29:50,229 --> 00:29:52,053
You’re lucky everyone was friends there.

346
00:29:53,116 --> 00:29:55,242
Or you’d be condemned by the whole nation now.

347
00:29:56,608 --> 00:30:00,827
And your big attempt to bring yourself this far would be in vain.

348
00:30:01,121 --> 00:30:04,533
So my work will not be affected, right?

349
00:30:14,127 --> 00:30:16,440
Can’t you see yourself, really?

350
00:30:18,730 --> 00:30:19,975
Trust me, Kawi.

351
00:30:21,689 --> 00:30:26,024
