380
00:33:15,733 --> 00:33:16,677
What number did you call?

381
00:33:18,694 --> 00:33:19,750
Your number, of course.

382
00:33:30,394 --> 00:33:32,041
I stopped using that number ages ago.

383
00:33:33,760 --> 00:33:34,863
I also told you that.

384
00:33:35,418 --> 00:33:36,416
But you just forgot.

385
00:33:38,431 --> 00:33:41,187
