397
00:34:23,642 --> 00:34:24,300
Huh?

398
00:34:26,090 --> 00:34:28,642
Why is everything messed up?

399
00:34:29,276 --> 00:34:30,291
Why?

400
00:34:35,434 --> 00:34:36,419
Why?

401
00:34:37,493 --> 00:34:39,947
Why is everything so messed up?

402
00:35:03,227 --> 00:35:04,723
You disappeared for months.

403
00:35:06,113 --> 00:35:07,710
This is how you’ve lived your life?

404
00:35:10,588 --> 00:35:11,493
Are you on break or what?

405
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:13,446
Don’t you have to go back to work?

406
00:35:14,556 --> 00:35:15,546
I just got here.

407
00:35:16,227 --> 00:35:17,388
Are you shooing me away now?

408
00:35:20,395 --> 00:35:23,857
I’ve just never seen you available in the past three years.

409
00:35:28,052 --> 00:35:29,876
Max canceled all my work.

410
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:35,500
He said I’m sick and need to be treated.

411
00:35:38,463 --> 00:35:40,463
Do you think I’m really sick as he said?

412
00:35:45,031 --> 00:35:45,842
I don’t know.

413
00:35:47,031 --> 00:35:48,472
You’re the only one who knows the answer.

414
00:35:51,892 --> 00:35:52,829
But honestly,

415
00:35:53,737 --> 00:35:56,666
