Huh?

420
00:36:15,693 --> 00:36:16,366
Come on.

421
00:36:16,744 --> 00:36:17,420
Let’s go.

422
00:36:17,881 --> 00:36:18,618
Woo!

423
00:36:19,021 --> 00:36:19,783
Go!

424
00:36:19,783 --> 00:36:20,410
Woo!!

425
00:36:22,876 --> 00:36:24,876
Woo!!

426
00:36:28,323 --> 00:36:29,023
Wait.

427
00:36:29,830 --> 00:36:31,735
You call this get in the water?

428
00:36:32,085 --> 00:36:32,780
Yes.

429
00:36:33,108 --> 00:36:34,413
It’s already fun like this.

430
00:36:34,616 --> 00:36:35,260
Come on.

431
00:36:37,025 --> 00:36:39,037
