432
00:36:39,270 --> 00:36:40,085
Seriously?

433
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:42,237
Why?

434
00:36:42,363 --> 00:36:43,514
I can do this.

435
00:36:43,514 --> 00:36:44,250
It’s fun already.

436
00:36:44,476 --> 00:36:45,468
