437
00:36:48,642 --> 00:36:49,298
Hey!

438
00:36:49,298 --> 00:36:49,990
No!

439
00:36:50,141 --> 00:36:52,709
Don’t.

440
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:55,127
No!

441
00:36:56,641 --> 00:36:58,086
Damn you!

442
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:02,713
