454
00:38:44,883 --> 00:38:45,579
It’s so good.

455
00:38:50,218 --> 00:38:51,385
You can eat.

456
00:38:51,737 --> 00:38:52,570
You’re probably not sick.

457
00:38:53,841 --> 00:38:57,499
Though I’m dying, I will never quit eating.

458
00:39:10,998 --> 00:39:12,390
How long are you gonna stay here?

459
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:16,138
None of your business.

460
00:39:17,788 --> 00:39:18,335
Hey.

461
00:39:18,812 --> 00:39:19,768
I asked you nicely.

462
00:39:22,714 --> 00:39:23,625
I don’t know.

463
00:39:24,454 --> 00:39:25,543
I might stay on

464
00:39:26,278 --> 00:39:27,658
until I know where to go next.

465
00:39:28,114 --> 00:39:29,045
Then I’ll move.

466
00:39:39,023 --> 00:39:40,240
I’m happy here.

467
00:39:40,675 --> 00:39:41,354
Okay?

468
00:39:43,684 --> 00:39:44,378
Are you?

469
00:40:04,864 --> 00:40:05,829
You should stop.

470
00:40:06,098 --> 00:40:07,672
