471
00:40:08,038 --> 00:40:08,858
Don’t let yourself get drunk.

472
00:40:09,160 --> 00:40:10,672
Just let me drink.

473
00:40:11,464 --> 00:40:13,132
I will just fall asleep if I’m drunk.

474
00:40:13,675 --> 00:40:14,431
That won’t hurt.

475
00:40:27,776 --> 00:40:28,475
Pisaeng.

476
00:40:35,086 --> 00:40:36,636
I’m truly glad

477
00:40:38,775 --> 00:40:40,423
