478
00:40:45,418 --> 00:40:46,275
Now you’re drunk.

479
00:40:47,788 --> 00:40:49,822
But I know what I’m saying.

480
00:40:53,585 --> 00:40:56,227
It’s me who’s glad to have you.

481
00:41:00,076 --> 00:41:01,481
Why would you be?

482
00:41:03,864 --> 00:41:07,526
You’re the one who has helped me with lots of things.

483
00:41:09,538 --> 00:41:13,383
I, however, can’t help you with anything.

484
00:41:17,299 --> 00:41:18,049
Who told you that?

485
00:41:21,179 --> 00:41:22,305
You helped me with one thing.

486
00:41:24,347 --> 00:41:27,363
It’s very huge and important.

487
00:41:29,500 --> 00:41:30,249
What is it?

488
00:41:33,876 --> 00:41:34,489
Not telling you.

489
00:41:35,898 --> 00:41:37,531
Hey, spill it.

490
00:41:38,147 --> 00:41:39,028
You don’t need to know.

491
00:41:52,073 --> 00:41:52,632
Here.

492
00:41:54,477 --> 00:41:55,066
