493
00:41:55,771 --> 00:41:57,618
Sing for me. I want to hear you sing.

494
00:41:58,304 --> 00:41:59,038
No.

495
00:41:59,038 --> 00:42:01,000
You’re a singer. You sing for me.

496
00:42:01,280 --> 00:42:02,340
But I wanna hear you sing.

497
00:42:02,672 --> 00:42:03,260
Take it.

498
00:42:03,260 --> 00:42:04,011
No.

