516
00:43:25,853 --> 00:43:29,373
♪ Is to stop loving you ♪

517
00:43:29,373 --> 00:43:31,890
♪ Tell me what to do ♪

518
00:43:32,113 --> 00:43:35,522
♪ Just tell me how to do ♪

