533
00:45:33,831 --> 00:45:35,240
It must be special, mustn’t it?

534
00:45:36,171 --> 00:45:37,303
It’s the 8th anniversary.

535
00:45:38,753 --> 00:45:39,932
You’re nuts.

536
00:45:40,697 --> 00:45:45,240
