537
00:45:45,702 --> 00:45:46,362
Well, look at yourself.

538
00:45:46,983 --> 00:45:48,634
You have anniversaries for everyone.

539
00:45:49,710 --> 00:45:50,864
Your dad’s death anniversary.

540
00:45:51,196 --> 00:45:52,166
Your anniversary with Pear.

541
00:45:52,890 --> 00:45:54,060
Your band anniversary with Fluke.

542
00:45:54,785 --> 00:45:57,584
